section.section:
"Disability benefit" does not include:
long-term care insurance;
a benefit that is payable based solely on a dismemberment of a covered individual;
benefits in a life insurance policy that operate to safeguard the contract from lapse or to provide a special surrender value, special benefit, or annuity in the event of total and permanent disability; or
benefits in a health insurance policy that operate to safeguard the contract from lapse due to disability.
